                            <comment id="14186631" author="kaspersor" created="Tue, 28 Oct 2014 09:17:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Actually this was originally thought of as a feature, since you can still invoke a CREATE TABLE statement on such a DataContext, which will then create the files. Maybe we should just document that?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14186653" author="ardlema" created="Tue, 28 Oct 2014 09:45:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fair enough! I did not take into account this scenario.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Anyway I think we should document this. Do you want me to add a phrase to the constructor javadoc that explain this??&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14186658" author="kaspersor" created="Tue, 28 Oct 2014 09:52:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sure, would be good!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
